definition: front/forward/ahead/first/top (followed by a number)/future/ago/before/BC (e.g. 前293年)/former/formerly
to come/to arrive/to come round/ever since/next

sentences.english: And the Gunners will fund it with their windfall for ex-skipper Patrick…
sentences.chinese: 槍手將會用賣出前隊長的前來收購他。

sentences.english: At this point of time, Hanwen arrives to arrest Shouye.
sentences.chinese: 這時漢文與偉民前來拘捕守業，衆人喫驚。

sentences.english: I thought it would raise a smile with people at the exhibition.
sentences.chinese: 我想它能給前來參觀展覽的人帶來笑容。

sentences.english: Hold them steadily before Him in faith and prayer.
sentences.chinese: 用信心和禱告帶到他面前來。

sentences.english: You seem to know this place vell well. Have you been here before?
sentences.chinese: 看來你非常熟悉這個地方，你以前來過這裏嗎？

sentences.english: When Jesus had entered Capernaum, a centurion came to him, asking for help.
sentences.chinese: 耶穌進了迦百農，有一個百夫長前來求助。

sentences.english: Thank you for letting us come by.
sentences.chinese: 謝謝你允許我們前來致哀。

sentences.english: Workshop director of high-strength comrades wholeheartedly welcome customers to negotiate business.
sentences.chinese: 車間主任高強同志竭誠歡迎廣大客戶前來洽談業務。

sentences.english: And the small mangrove forests left the camp to identify reactive nakamura.
sentences.chinese: 營左押着小林澤前來指認中村功。

sentences.english: I got to the Tanghu middle school three weeks ago.
sentences.chinese: 我在三週前來到了棠湖中學。

sentences.english: Bring the tribe of Levi and present them to Aaron the priest to assist him.
sentences.chinese: 你使利未支派近前來，站在祭司亞倫面前好服事他。

sentences.english: One day, his aunt came to beg for forgiveness.
sentences.chinese: 一日，密勒日巴的姑母前來祈求原諒。

sentences.english: Steady rollin woman gonna come my way.
sentences.chinese: 穩步輥女子前來自首途中。

sentences.english: Drogon has come this way before, she realized.
sentences.chinese: 卓耿以前來過這裏，她意識到了。

sentences.english: In the first quarter, he drove, scooped the ball left-handed under Yao's arms, off the glass and into the hoop.
sentences.chinese: 在第一節的時候在姚明面突破前來了個漂亮的上籃。

sentences.english: Elijah went before the people and said, 'How long will you waver between two opinions?
sentences.chinese: 以利亞前來對衆民說，你們心持兩意要到幾時呢？
